# ULDA-NC Headers (v1.0)
This sheet provides multiple language-specific header variants compatible with Section 3.1 of ULDA-NC-1.0.
Pick ONE per file type. Prefer the SPDX one-liner when your tooling supports it.

## Canonical Options (use one)
**A) SPDX (preferred):**
```
// SPDX-License-Identifier: ULDA-NC-1.0
```
*Alt for custom SPDX registries:*
```
// SPDX-License-Identifier: LicenseRef-ULDA-NC-1.0
```

**B) Two short lines:**
```
// Licensed under ULDA-NC-1.0 — see LICENSE
// © 2025 Mark Shaposhnik / ZeroAM
```

**C) Full minimal (multi-line allowed as appropriate):**
```
// This file is licensed under ULDA-NC-1.0 — see LICENSE.
// © 2025 Mark Shaposhnik / Shaposhnik Oam & Services IT (d/b/a ZeroAM)
```

**Modification mark (when distributing modified code):**
```
// This file/software has been modified by ACME Corp on 2025-10-01.
```

---

## Language-Specific Examples

### C / C++ / Java / C# / Go (line comments)
```
// SPDX-License-Identifier: ULDA-NC-1.0
```

### C / C++ / Java / C# / Go (block)
```
/*
 * Licensed under ULDA-NC-1.0 — see LICENSE
 * © 2025 Mark Shaposhnik / ZeroAM
 */
```

### JavaScript / TypeScript
```
// SPDX-License-Identifier: ULDA-NC-1.0
```

### Python
```
# SPDX-License-Identifier: ULDA-NC-1.0
```

### Bash / Shell
```
# SPDX-License-Identifier: ULDA-NC-1.0
```

### Rust
```
// SPDX-License-Identifier: ULDA-NC-1.0
```

### Swift / Kotlin
```
// SPDX-License-Identifier: ULDA-NC-1.0
```

### Ruby
```
# SPDX-License-Identifier: ULDA-NC-1.0
```

### PHP
```php
<?php
// SPDX-License-Identifier: ULDA-NC-1.0
```

### HTML
```html
<!-- SPDX-License-Identifier: ULDA-NC-1.0 -->
```

### CSS
```css
/* SPDX-License-Identifier: ULDA-NC-1.0 */
```

### XML
```xml
<!-- SPDX-License-Identifier: ULDA-NC-1.0 -->
```

### SQL
```sql
-- SPDX-License-Identifier: ULDA-NC-1.0
```

### PowerShell
```
# SPDX-License-Identifier: ULDA-NC-1.0
```

### Windows Batch (.bat)
```
:: SPDX-License-Identifier: ULDA-NC-1.0
REM Alternatively: REM SPDX-License-Identifier: ULDA-NC-1.0
```

### MATLAB / Octave
```
% SPDX-License-Identifier: ULDA-NC-1.0
```

### R
```
# SPDX-License-Identifier: ULDA-NC-1.0
```

### LaTeX
```
% SPDX-License-Identifier: ULDA-NC-1.0
```

### YAML / TOML
```
# SPDX-License-Identifier: ULDA-NC-1.0
```

### INI
```
; SPDX-License-Identifier: ULDA-NC-1.0
```

---

## Manifests Without Comments (e.g., JSON)
Plain JSON does not support comments. Suggested approaches:
- put the license file in the repo (e.g., LICENSE-ULDA-NC-1.0.txt) and set
  "license": "SEE LICENSE IN LICENSE-ULDA-NC-1.0.txt" in package.json;
- or include a short note in README and in your build tooling.

**package.json example:**
```json
{
  "name": "@zeroam/yourpkg",
  "version": "1.0.0",
  "license": "SEE LICENSE IN LICENSE-ULDA-NC-1.0.txt"
}
```

**NOTICE example for binaries:**
```
This product includes components licensed under ULDA-NC-1.0.
© 2025 Mark Shaposhnik / Shaposhnik Oam & Services IT (d/b/a ZeroAM)
See the LICENSE-ULDA-NC-1.0.txt file for terms.
```
